<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="S" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Supper-time" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Supper-time,</orth> the time of the evening meal: <bibl n="shak. tmp 3.1.95" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. III, 1, 95</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. shr 4.3.192" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. IV, 3, 192</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. shr 5.2.128" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 2, 128</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 1.4.59" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A I, 4, 59</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 5.3.47" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 V, 3, 47</bibl> <cit><quote>(it's s., my lord; it's nine o' clock).</quote> <bibl n="shak. mac 3.1.44" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. III, 1, 44</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. oth 4.2.249" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. IV, 2, 249</bibl>. <cit><quote>at s.</quote> <bibl n="shak. mv 2.2.215" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. II, 2, 215</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>soon at s.</quote> <bibl n="shak. err 3.2.179" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. III, 2, 179</bibl></cit> (cf. <emph>Soon</emph>). <cit><quote>in s.</quote> <bibl n="shak. mv 2.4.1" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. II, 4, 1</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>